---

<section id="cta" class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-azul relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-verde rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
      ¿Listo para no perder ni una reserva más?
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Solicita una demo y descubre cómo Bukiq puede ayudar a tu restaurante a atender reservas las 24 horas del día, los 7 días de la semana.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://cal.eu/bukiq/30min"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-verde text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-verde/90 transition-colors text-base"
      >
        Solicitar demo gratuita
        <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <span class="text-white/60 text-sm">Sin compromiso · Reserva tu demo de 30 min</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
